title: Young Indiana Jones deleted Old Indy bumpers
description:
When Young Indiana Jones first aired in the early 90s, the first season and some second season episodes had bumpers that featured an old Indiana Jones.

But, when the show was released on VHS tape and DVDS in the late 90s and 2000s, the 45 min epidsodes were stripped of these bumpers so they could be combined together to make 90 min movies.

Not every episode had these bumpers.

These bumpers were not included on the DVDs, not even as bonus deleted scenes extras.

All videos were taken from youtube and are not mine.

I did edit, alter them, combined some and rename them to fit my personal tastes.

If you enjoy these, please visit StooTV on youtube to see the original versions.

His youtube page is awesome and should be visited by you.
